\pi1 Hafi lomi i peretoo, waduhero (Hell): Lk 16:23; Mk 9:43
\pi1 Hagua (Love): Mk 12:30; 12:31
\pi1 Haidaa (God): watauda
\pi1 Haidaa sifisifi (Idol): Ac 15:20
\pi1 Hani'u (Devil): Mt 4:1; Jn 13:2
\pi1 Haparaia (Kingdom): Mk 1:15; Mk 10:23; Mk 12:34
\pi1 Haperararaia (Persecute): Mt 5:11; Lk 21:12; Ac 9:4
\pi1 Harenua lomi i pedutoo (Eternal life): Mk 10:30; Jn 6:68
\pi1 Hatofaa puda (Kiss): Lk 22:48; Ro 16:16
\pi1 Hawafolo (Cross): Mk 15:32
\pi1 Hawegi (Bless): Ge 1:22; Mt 5:44; Mk 10 16
\pi1 Hawera (Glory): Mk 8:38; Ac 7:55
