\pi1 Mania (Tempt): Mk 1:13
\pi1 Marapuaa unu (Conscience): Jn 16:8; Heb 9:9
\pi1 Mefi, fanunua (Vision): Acts 9:10
\pi1 Moro'aa hudii wawanei (Circumcision): Ac 7:8
\pi1 Nafi (Servant): Mk 12:2; Lk 2:29
\pi1 Nanamaia (Covet): Ac 20:33; Ro 13:9
\pi1 Narafawe'i (Believe/faith): Mk 2:5; Ac 16:31
\pi1 Naranara, laloo ia, harenua (Soul): Mk 8:36; Ac 2:27; Mk 14:34
\pi1 Na'uu Rama'a (Son of Man): Mk 8:31
\pi1 O'onaia unu (Hope): Ac 23:6; 1Co 13:13; Eph 4:4
\pi1 Otalai nenera (Disciple): Mk 2:15
\pi1 Pa'ai (Perish): Mt 18:14; Lk 13:35
\pi1 Paniaa pani (Deacon): 1Ti 3:12
\pi1 Papaditai (Sanctify): Mt 23:19; Jn 17:17
\pi1 Pentecost: Ac 2:1
